<appendix><title>Running on XBOX</title>
<subtitle>how to burn and run a dyne:bolic for XBOX game consoles</subtitle>

<para>
In order to have a CD that is bootable on XBOX you must check the DVD reader
you have on your xbox. Some older models can only boot REWRITABLE CDs.
</para>

<para>
If you have a NTSC tv connected then you can have some problems on
your visualization at boot - just open an XTERM and write :
<screen>
<prompt>[d:b] ~ # </prompt><userinput>xbv -NTSC -auto 640 480 12.00 9.00</userinput> <lineannotation><keycap>[Enter]</keycap></lineannotation>
</screen>
to have it fixed.
</para>

